title: [Bug]:  getResultOutputFile switch miss the resource 'MissingGetResultFileError'
body:
### Issue Description
https://github.com/dotnet/msbuild/pull/9640
Internal MSBuild Error: Missing resource 'MissingGetResultFileError'

### Steps to Reproduce

msbuild ConsoleApplication1.sln -getProperty:Bar -getResultOutputFile:

### Expected Behavior

Add the resource MissingGetItemError in  the resource file
